@startuml seq_sync_payroll
!theme plain
title Sequence Diagram: Sync & Get Payroll

skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Manager/Admin" as Manager
participant "React SPA" as Client
participant "Kong API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Salary Service" as Salary
database "PostgreSQL (HA)" as PG

Manager -> Client : Access /payroll, select Month/Year
Client -> Gateway : GET /api/payroll/:year/:month
Gateway -> Salary : Route Request (With JWT Token)

Salary -> Salary : Decode & Verify JWT Token

par Concurrent Data Fetching
    Salary -> PG : Query Users (Status: ACTIVE)
    Salary -> PG : Query Attendance Logs (By Month)
    Salary -> PG : Query Leave Requests (Status: APPROVED)
    Salary -> PG : Query System Settings (Penalties, Working Hours)
end

Note over Salary: Calculate Net Salary (syncPayrollRealtime())\n1. Calc Standard Work Days\n2. Deduct Late/Absence Penalties\n3. Add OT Bonuses

Salary -> PG : INSERT/UPDATE monthly_payrolls (Status: DRAFT)\n(ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE)
Salary -> Client : Return Payroll List Data
Client -> Manager : Render Payroll Table UI
@enduml